{"tid":1594853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"9.1東涌白衣男揮刀追斬市民 警隔24日終於拉人","createTime":"2019-09-25T18:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T00:37:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"84ea3ee87a2022a32b6a747e20bda9bbf3558ebf","tid":1594853,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:28:19.000Z","msg":"9.1網民發起「901機場見」活動，大批市民在機場聚集，一度爆發警民衝突，機場一帶交通近乎癱瘓，大批示威者徒步離開機場到東涌，部份人再行出青馬大橋巴士站。當日下午5時，逸東邨一名白衣人持刀追斬示威者及街坊，市民受驚爭相走避。事隔24日，今日警方表示，主動調查有關案件後，今午於逸東邨一單位拘捕45歲姓蔡男子，涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器。蔡已被暫控一項「藏有攻擊性武器」罪，案件將於明日上午在西九龍裁判法院提堂。案件交由大嶼山警區反三合會行動組人員跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190925/60084570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F60084570&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTpKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=ef1a0bae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F60084570&h=af81533a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190925/60084570</a>"},{"pid":"4f4ec2ee361651cc1c791f6fec00831c5e7f75e5","tid":1594853,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:29:53.000Z","msg":"關公?"},{"pid":"17d8982effc6a07819a635b6f05b27884dc10fb3","tid":1594853,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f4ec2ee361651cc1c791f6fec00831c5e7f75e5","tid":1594853,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:29:53.000Z","msg":"關公?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7c3df505c59f816c447115832152ecf8f66894","tid":15